<%# app/views/pages/about.html.erb %>
<% content_for :title, "About — The Anchorpoint Retreat" %>
<% content_for :description, "Learn the story behind The Anchorpoint Retreat — a private mountain chalet in Alma, Colorado for focused work, quiet resets, and year-round mountain adventure." %>

<section class="section banner-home" style="background-image: url('<%= asset_path('backg-retreat-1920-900.jpg') %>'); background-position: center center !important; min-height: 50vh;">
    <div class="hero-container">
        <div class="banner-home-container text-center">
            <h1 class="banner-home-title">Our Story</h1>
            <p class="banner-home-excerpt">A Modern Alpine Chalet Near Mosquito Pass</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <div class="hero-container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <span class="sub-heading">About Us</span>
                <h2>A Place to Find Your Anchor</h2>
                <p>The Anchorpoint Retreat is a contemporary mountain chalet built in 2022, located in the quiet alpine valley of Alma, Colorado — about 5 minutes from town and about 30 minutes from Breckenridge. Set near the base of Mosquito Pass, the property was created as a space for focused work, quiet resets, small leadership retreats, and year-round mountain adventure.</p>
                <p>With 1,080 square feet of thoughtfully designed living space, soaring 16-foot ceilings, beetle kill pine accents, and an electric fireplace, the chalet offers modern comfort in a peaceful setting. The open layout includes a full kitchen with butcher block counters and stainless steel appliances, one bedroom, one bathroom, and a spacious loft that works equally well as additional sleeping space, a workspace, a reading nook, or a creative studio.</p>
                <p>The surrounding area offers world-class skiing at Breckenridge, hiking and scenic drives over Mosquito Pass, trout fishing in the South Park region, and wildlife viewing right outside the door. It is best suited for short-stay and part-time use, consistent with county guidelines — ideal for founder retreats, executive resets, strategy weekends, remote-work stays, couples getaways, and small-group outdoor adventures.</p>

                <h3 class="mt-4">Our Philosophy</h3>
                <p>We believe in the power of stepping away to see clearly. This chalet was built not as a luxury resort, but as a place where clear thinking, meaningful conversation, and genuine connection can happen naturally. The mountains provide the backdrop; the space provides the quiet; guests bring the purpose.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <div class="card p-4 text-center">
                    <%= image_tag "dummy-img-600x600.jpg", alt: "Property Host", class: "img-fluid rounded-circle mb-3", style: "max-width: 200px;" %>
                    <h3 class="heading-sm">Meet Your Host</h3>
                    <p>We're based locally and dedicated to making your stay seamless and rewarding. Whether you're here for focused work, mountain adventure, or a quiet reset — we're here to help you make the most of it.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section-px-pt-small banner-service">
    <div class="hero-container">
        <h2 class="accent-color-2 text-center mb-4">Location Highlights</h2>
        <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-3 grid-gap-2">
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card p-4 text-center">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-snowflake fa-3x accent-color mb-3"></i>
                    <h3 class="heading-sm">Breckenridge Skiing</h3>
                    <p>About 30 minutes to Breckenridge Ski Resort — world-class skiing, snowboarding, and winter activities.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card p-4 text-center">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-mountain fa-3x accent-color mb-3"></i>
                    <h3 class="heading-sm">Mosquito Pass</h3>
                    <p>One of Colorado's highest scenic passes, right at the doorstep — ideal for hiking, 4x4 exploring, and photography.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card p-4 text-center">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-fish fa-3x accent-color mb-3"></i>
                    <h3 class="heading-sm">Fishing &amp; Outdoor Rec</h3>
                    <p>Trout fishing near Fairplay, hiking trails, wildlife viewing, and wide-open alpine scenery in every direction.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
